{"tid":1635599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：連登巴打英文game 向國際宣傳反送中 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:03:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40dc8c9d9b0ba6232a3740b8c020576927bcb10f","tid":1635599,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191007/20782604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782604&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=58be3b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782604&h=7f85a1ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191007/20782604</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：連登巴打英文game<br />\n向國際宣傳反送中 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191007/large/1570381997_e1a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570381997_e1a1.jpg&h=4f09f9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次反送中運動中，國際文宣真係好厲害，呢個當然係連登攬炒巴同佢團隊嘅功勞，但亦有連登巴打提過，單靠海外廣告可能未必夠，特別係對外國年輕人，網上文宣都好重要，有連登巴竟然整咗個英文嘅角色扮演手遊，等外國人可以透過呢個game，由6月9日反送中運動開始，了解港人點樣走過成個抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文字RPG 玩家買裝備<br />\n<br />\n呢隻叫「The Revolution of Our Times I」嘅文字RPG ，主要用文字方式，由你扮演不同角色做不同決定，去體驗由6.9開始點樣參與運動，而每個決定都有機會影響故事嘅發展同選擇，例如選擇走佬離開香港，就冇得選擇去前線，遊戲亦有得買裝備，提升力量去前線，又有不同任務可以打。<br />\n<br />\n創作呢隻game巴打話，搞呢隻game係為爭取國際嘅支持，因為佢想全世界嘅人都有機會了解、體驗反送中運動，但佢係冇可能買幾萬張機票，叫晒全世界人嚟香港參與，所以就寫咗呢隻以文字為主嘅RPG，希望可以畀所有人都有機會參加呢場時代革命，體驗一下香港人由6月9號開始所經歷過嘅嘢。而呢隻game叫「The Revolution of Our Times I」，因為佢預仲有第二同第三集，暫時就只有android版，可以去Google Play store下載遊戲，巴打仲話遊戲嘅八成收入，每個月尾會捐畀星火。<br />\n<br />\n李八方 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：建制區選海報 人瘦logo細 (李八方)"},{"pid":"1657ffacb3a11c8711f03282715a71a511b44b8a","tid":1635599,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"402f427a95f2851d305fe419d0b3d106debe360c","tid":1635599,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3063a54982c81c6593f9ab4f7feaa727a4f8b170","tid":1635599,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隻game俾人隊落架呀，快另開post救佢!</span>"},{"pid":"1e8bb433e3089af0c81667f32147b886d615d92c","tid":1635599,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人救下佢?</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/10/revolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F10%2Frevolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=80a547e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/10/revolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store/</a>"}]}